  "html_url": "https://github.com/CGCL-codes/Rattrap",
  "description": "Rattrap is a container-based cloud platform for mobile code offloading and provides mobile code runtime environments through Cloud Android Container. In this framework, the cloud runtime is not VM or JVM. We use OS-level virtualization \"Linux Container (LXC)\" as the runtime for mobile code. For the purpose of running android code in x86 GNU-Linux server, we have modified android source code and the linux kernel it uses. The modification work is based on Android-x86 project. With our effort, android OS can finally run in the ordinary linux containers!",
